 2023-07822023-07-26PMO
ActPhysical Activity and Sport Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Sport and Persons with Disabilities as the Minister for the Purposes of the Physical Activity and Sport Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2018-1014 of July 18, 2018 and Order in Council P.C. 2021-944 of October 26, 2021; and (2) designating the Minister of SPORT AND PERSONS WITH DISABILITIES, a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the PHYSICAL ACTIVITY AND SPORT ACT.
